<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4442.1.12>
    bibo:endPage "193" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2018-06-29" ;
    bibo:startPage "187" ;
    bibo:volume "4442" ;
    dc:creator "Jiao, Ke-Long; Wang, Hao; Huang, Jun-Hao; Han, Pei-Jin; Zhang, Long-Wa; Jiao, Xue; Wu, Zhi-Hui; Zhang, Jing; Wang, Yuan-Hong; Bu, Wen-Jun; Kolesik, Peter" ;
    dc:date "2018" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Contarinia (Diptera: Cecidomyiidae) damaging inflorescence of Carya cathayensis (Juglandaceae) in China" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301430>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301432>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301434> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301430>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–5. Contarinia caryafloralis. 1, 2, 4, 5: male; 3: female. (1) palpus, (2) 3rd flagellomere, (3) 3rd flagellomere, (4) wing, (5) front tarsal claw with empodium and pulvillus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1301430/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301432>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6–12. Contarinia caryafloralis sp. nov. 6, 7: male; 8–10: female; 11, 12: larva. (6) terminalia in dorsal view, (7) terminalia in ventral view, (8) postabdomen in lateral view, (9) end of ovipositor in ventral view showing cerci and hypoproct, (10) end of ovipositor in dorsolateral view showing cerci and partly hypoproct, (11) sternal spatula with adjacent papillae, (12) last two abdominal segments of larva in dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1301432/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1301434>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–16. Infestation of Chinese Hickory by Contarinia caryafloralis sp. nov. (13) damaged female inflorescence, (14) mature larvae feeding within female flower (infested flower was cut open to reveal larvae), (15) damaged male inflorescences, (16) young larvae feeding on male flowers." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1301434/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

